INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (25,1,'2023-10-04 07:21:03','2023-10-04 07:21:03','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Amidst the tranquil rustling of leaves in the dense forest, a solitary cabin stood as a haven of solitude. The golden rays of the setting sun filtered through the emerald canopy, casting a warm, ethereal glow on the moss-covered ground. Birds sang their evening serenades, while a gentle breeze whispered secrets to the swaying trees. Inside the cabin, the crackling fireplace provided a cozy ambiance, its dancing flames casting flickering shadows that danced across the weathered wooden walls. In this secluded retreat, time seemed to slow, allowing the weary soul to find respite and reconnect with nature\'s timeless rhythms.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:comments -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-comments\"><!-- wp:comments-title /-->\n\n<!-- wp:comment-template -->\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"40px\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:40px\"><!-- wp:avatar {\"size\":40,\"style\":{\"border\":{\"radius\":\"20px\"}}} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:comment-author-name {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0px\",\"bottom\":\"0px\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px\"><!-- wp:comment-date {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:comment-edit-link {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:comment-content /-->\n\n<!-- wp:comment-reply-link {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n<!-- /wp:comment-template -->\n\n<!-- wp:comments-pagination -->\n<!-- wp:comments-pagination-previous /-->\n\n<!-- wp:comments-pagination-numbers /-->\n\n<!-- wp:comments-pagination-next /-->\n<!-- /wp:comments-pagination -->\n\n<!-- wp:post-comments-form /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:comments -->','Post 1','','publish','open','open','','post-1','','','2023-11-01 08:20:56','2023-11-01 08:20:56','',0,'http://firstexample.local/?p=25',0,'post','',1);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (26,1,'2023-10-04 07:21:03','2023-10-04 07:21:03','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Amidst the tranquil rustling of leaves in the dense forest, a solitary cabin stood as a haven of solitude. The golden rays of the setting sun filtered through the emerald canopy, casting a warm, ethereal glow on the moss-covered ground. Birds sang their evening serenades, while a gentle breeze whispered secrets to the swaying trees. Inside the cabin, the crackling fireplace provided a cozy ambiance, its dancing flames casting flickering shadows that danced across the weathered wooden walls. In this secluded retreat, time seemed to slow, allowing the weary soul to find respite and reconnect with nature\'s timeless rhythms.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Post 1','','inherit','closed','closed','','25-revision-v1','','','2023-10-04 07:21:03','2023-10-04 07:21:03','',25,'http://firstexample.local/?p=26',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (27,1,'2023-10-04 07:21:43','2023-10-04 07:21:43','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the heart of the bustling city, the neon lights painted the night with a kaleidoscope of colors. People hurriedly navigated the crowded streets, lost in their thoughts or the glow of their smartphones. The cacophony of car horns and chatter filled the air, creating a symphony of urban life. Skyscrapers pierced the sky, their glass facades reflecting the ever-changing cityscape. Amidst the chaos, hidden gems of street art adorned forgotten alleyways, offering a glimpse of creativity amidst the concrete jungle.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Post 2','','publish','open','open','','post-2','','','2023-10-04 07:21:43','2023-10-04 07:21:43','',0,'http://firstexample.local/?p=27',0,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (28,1,'2023-10-04 07:21:43','2023-10-04 07:21:43','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the heart of the bustling city, the neon lights painted the night with a kaleidoscope of colors. People hurriedly navigated the crowded streets, lost in their thoughts or the glow of their smartphones. The cacophony of car horns and chatter filled the air, creating a symphony of urban life. Skyscrapers pierced the sky, their glass facades reflecting the ever-changing cityscape. Amidst the chaos, hidden gems of street art adorned forgotten alleyways, offering a glimpse of creativity amidst the concrete jungle.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Post 2','','inherit','closed','closed','','27-revision-v1','','','2023-10-04 07:21:43','2023-10-04 07:21:43','',27,'http://firstexample.local/?p=28',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (29,1,'2023-10-04 07:21:56','2023-10-04 07:21:56','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The vast desert stretched endlessly in all directions, an unforgiving expanse of golden sand dunes. The scorching sun hung high in the sky, casting a relentless heat upon the arid landscape. Mirage-like illusions danced on the horizon, teasing travelers with promises of water and shade. The only signs of life were the hardy desert flora and the occasional lizard darting across the hot sand. Yet, in this desolate beauty, there was a profound sense of serenity and a connection to the ancient rhythms of the Earth.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Post 3','','publish','open','open','','post-3','','','2023-10-04 07:21:56','2023-10-04 07:21:56','',0,'http://firstexample.local/?p=29',0,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (30,1,'2023-10-04 07:21:56','2023-10-04 07:21:56','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The vast desert stretched endlessly in all directions, an unforgiving expanse of golden sand dunes. The scorching sun hung high in the sky, casting a relentless heat upon the arid landscape. Mirage-like illusions danced on the horizon, teasing travelers with promises of water and shade. The only signs of life were the hardy desert flora and the occasional lizard darting across the hot sand. Yet, in this desolate beauty, there was a profound sense of serenity and a connection to the ancient rhythms of the Earth.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Post 3','','inherit','closed','closed','','29-revision-v1','','','2023-10-04 07:21:56','2023-10-04 07:21:56','',29,'http://firstexample.local/?p=30',0,'revision','',0);
